summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 11W, page 53 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in that portion of Government Lot 5, and also that portion of Lots 1 and 2, Block 7, of Seattle Tide Lands, in Section 11, Township 25 North, Range 3 East W.M.
